#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
#define gc getchar_unlocked

main() {
	int T,j,i;
	char c;
	scanf("%d",&T);
	gc();
	while(T--) {
		int b[26]={0};
		c=gc();
		while(c!=10) {
			if((c>='A' && c<='Z') || (c>='a' && c<='z'))
				b[tolower(c)-97]++;
			c=gc();
		}
		int max=0;
		for(i=0;i<26;i++)
			if(b[i]>=b[max])
				max=i;
		printf("%c\n",max+97);
	}
}
